<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="tr">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>İletişim Sayfası</title>

    <!-- Google Material Icons -->
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/icon?family=Material+Icons" rel="stylesheet">
    <!-- Font Awesome (ikonlar için) -->
    <script src="https://kit.fontawesome.com/a076d05399.js" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>

    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            color: #333;
            background-color: #E3F2FD; /* Açık mavi arka plan */
        }

        .iletisim-container {
            min-height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            padding: 50px 20px;
        }

        .iletisim-card {
            background: white;
            padding: 40px;
            border-radius: 12px;
            box-shadow: 0px 4px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            max-width: 800px;
            text-align: center;
        }

            .iletisim-card h2 {
                color: #0277BD;
                font-weight: bold;
            }

        .iletisim-info {
            margin-top: 20px;
            font-size: 18px;
        }

            .iletisim-info p {
                font-weight: bold;
                font-size: 20px;
                margin: 15px 0;
                color: #0277BD;
            }


        .instagram {
            background-color: #00796B;
            padding: 10px;
            border-radius: 8px;
        }

        .linkedin {
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, #6a11cb, #2575fc);
            padding: 10px;
            border-radius: 8px;
        }

        .email {
            background-color: #FF6F00;
            padding: 10px;
            border-radius: 8px;
        }


        .iletisim-info .instagram,
        .iletisim-info .linkedin,
        .iletisim-info .email,
        .iletisim-info .phone {
            color: black;
        }


        .iletisim-info a {
            text-decoration: none;
            color: black;
            font-weight: bold;
        }

            .iletisim-info a:hover {
                color: #01579B;
            }

        .icon {
            font-size: 24px;
            margin-right: 10px;
            color: white;
        }

        .map-container {
            margin-top: 30px;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="iletisim-container">
        <div class="iletisim-card">
            <h2>📞 İletişim</h2>
            <p>Bizimle iletişime geçmek için aşağıdaki bilgileri kullanabilirsiniz.</p>

            <div class="iletisim-info">
                <p class="instagram">İnstagram Hesabımız</p>
                <p><i class="icon fab fa-instagram"></i> <a href="https://www.instagram.com/oneteknoloji" target="_blank">oneteknoloji</a></p>

                <p class="linkedin">LinkedIn Hesabımız</p>
                <p><i class="icon fab fa-linkedin"></i> <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/company/oneteknoloji" target="_blank">oneteknoloji</a></p>

                <p class="email">Mailimiz</p>
                <p><i class="icon fas fa-envelope"></i> <a href="mailto:info@oneteknoloji.com">info@oneteknoloji.com</a></p>

                <p class="phone">
                    <i class="icon fas fa-phone"></i> <a href="tel:+902163472121">(0216) 347 21 21</a>
                </p>
            </div>

            <h3>📍 Konumumuz</h3>
            <p>Caferağa, Mühürdar Cd. No:76, 34710 Kadıköy/İstanbul</p>

            <div class="map-container">
                <iframe width="100%"
                        height="300"
                        frameborder="0"
                        style="border:0; border-radius:10px; box-shadow: 0px 4px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);"
                        src="https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d3125.3797993209365!2d29.02574377643756!3d40.98785327139157!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x14cac78c9ebf1c69%3A0xc61e3652aa1e491d!2sM%C3%BCh%C3%BCrdar%20Cd.%20No%3A76%2C%2034710%20Kadık%C3%B6y%2F%C4%B0stanbul!5e0!3m2!1str!2str!4v1700000000000"
                        allowfullscreen>
                </iframe>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
